{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTM5MzQyMjUy", "number": 2544, "title": "[DOCS] Client Testing Guidelines", "bodyText": "Motivation and Context\n\n\nWe have not yet written down any guidelines for client testing. The goal of this PR is to change this.\nDescription\n\nAdded a client testing section to the client guidelines", "createdAt": "2020-12-14T10:33:43Z", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/2544", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "26087a5b7dd9cea799057d6a9fcf1e288fc9a26b"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-12-17T20:35:47Z", "author": {"login": "stefanwaldhauser"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 18, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdmDPyZgH2gAyNTM5MzQyMjUyOjIwNDJhYmY1ZjBiNmEwMjgxYjk2NWM5YmJkN2M4MTU5ZmM2ZDAxYzI=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdnJpX0gFqTU1NDk2Njk1Mg==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "2042abf5f0b6a0281b965c9bbd7c8159fc6d01c2", "author": {"user": {"login": "stefanwaldhauser", "name": "Stefan Waldhauser"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/2042abf5f0b6a0281b965c9bbd7c8159fc6d01c2", "committedDate": "2020-12-14T10:33:19Z", "message": "Wrote some client testing guidelines"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "4ef4aa16e8b968d3138f81afc323bed7690cbd6e", "author": {"user": {"login": "stefanwaldhauser", "name": "Stefan Waldhauser"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/4ef4aa16e8b968d3138f81afc323bed7690cbd6e", "committedDate": "2020-12-14T10:43:01Z", "message": "Added sinon sandbox guideline"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "ab35ffa8a82376d26e71d992864c3673451624a1", "author": {"user": {"login": "FrankeLukas", "name": "Lukas Franke"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/ab35ffa8a82376d26e71d992864c3673451624a1", "committedDate": "2020-12-14T15:34:44Z", "message": "Fix compiler warnings"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTUxNjAxMjkx", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/2544#pullrequestreview-551601291", "createdAt": "2020-12-14T16:50:56Z", "commit": {"oid": "ab35ffa8a82376d26e71d992864c3673451624a1"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0xMi0xNFQxNjo1MDo1NlrOIFaACA==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0xMi0xNFQxNjo1MDo1NlrOIFaACA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU0MjUzOTc4NA==", "bodyText": "We should imo add import { ComponentFixture, TestBed } from '@angular/core/testing'; to the import statements as we require ComponentFixture here and TestBed below.", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/2544#discussion_r542539784", "createdAt": "2020-12-14T16:50:56Z", "author": {"login": "FrankeLukas"}, "path": "docs/dev/guidelines/client.rst", "diffHunk": "@@ -90,4 +90,118 @@ Some general aspects:\n We use ``prettier`` to style code automatically and ``eslint`` to find additional issues.\n You can find the corresponding commands to invoked those tools in ``package.json``.\n \n+9. Testing\n+===========\n+\n+If you are new to client testing, it is highly recommended that you work through the testing part of the angular tutorial: https://angular.io/guide/testing.\n+\n+We use Jest (https://jestjs.io/) as our client testing framework.\n+\n+There are different tools available to support client testing. A common combination you can see in our codebase is:\n+\n+- Sinon (https://sinonjs.org/) for creating test spies, stubs and mocks\n+- Chai (https://www.chaijs.com/) with Sinon Chai (https://github.com/domenic/sinon-chai) for assertions.\n+- NgMocks (https://www.npmjs.com/package/ng-mocks) for mocking the dependencies of an angular component.\n+\n+The most basic test looks similar to this:\n+\n+ .. code:: ts\n+\n+    import * as chai from 'chai';\n+    import * as sinonChai from 'sinon-chai';\n+    import * as sinon from 'sinon';\n+\n+    chai.use(sinonChai);\n+    const expect = chai.expect;\n+\n+    describe('SomeComponent', () => {\n+        let someComponentFixture: ComponentFixture<SomeComponent>;", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "ab35ffa8a82376d26e71d992864c3673451624a1"}, "originalPosition": 29}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "8ef8801be305abe89bd8761c506960c21cf11298", "author": {"user": {"login": "stefanwaldhauser", "name": "Stefan Waldhauser"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/8ef8801be305abe89bd8761c506960c21cf11298", "committedDate": "2020-12-14T18:46:24Z", "message": "Modified docu"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "07d091c2b5b4e77fcb6a466dbf0238c424c17296", "author": {"user": {"login": "stefanwaldhauser", "name": "Stefan Waldhauser"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/07d091c2b5b4e77fcb6a466dbf0238c424c17296", "committedDate": "2020-12-14T18:46:44Z", "message": "Merge remote-tracking branch 'origin/doc/client-testing' into doc/client-testing"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTUxOTAzOTM3", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/2544#pullrequestreview-551903937", "createdAt": "2020-12-14T21:22:49Z", "commit": {"oid": "07d091c2b5b4e77fcb6a466dbf0238c424c17296"}, "state": "DISMISSED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTUxOTExMTM2", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/2544#pullrequestreview-551911136", "createdAt": "2020-12-14T21:33:21Z", "commit": {"oid": "07d091c2b5b4e77fcb6a466dbf0238c424c17296"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}